{"tid":892088,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(減肥)開始一星期分享&求教","createTime":"2018-11-06T15:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T13:45:15.000Z","uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3a2e2d949df834cb30ebb3d8137d564dd1086c","tid":892088,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"先利申: 175cm, 81kg, A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近有意認識一位公司女同事同埋交往，但自己向來有肚腩，喺身材上自覺未能吸引異性而自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以上月尾開始的起心肝減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目標70kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先share吓過去一星期嘅膳食方面，每日午晚兩餐多菜少肉例牌，同埋就係只食細半碗飯碗份量嘅飯。飯裡撈埋糙米食。頭兩日係難挨啲，特別是易肚餓想加料或者買其他嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要忍著。到第三日開始就習慣，餓嘅程度可以忍到下一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因此可以skip埋宵夜呢個最易致肥嘅一餐。順帶一提早餐食麥皮為主，偶然同家人飲早茶不過都keep著食唔多。食完早餐返工搭車都盡量企下，有吉位都冇坐。<br />\n<br />\n另外而家多咗個習慣，就係午晚餐後都會落街度步大約半粒鐘，唔會食完就坐落去甚至灘喺度。度完步返上樓基本上接著就有屎屙好舒暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飯後活動下助長消化果然係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使返工期間，lunch完都會圍著寫字樓大廈行幾圈先返埋位。<br />\n<br />\n仲有運動，逢放假都會去行行山徑，全程約75分鐘，出返一身汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日試咗圍住運動場緩步跑10圈又係一個good choice. 總知件衫唔濕曬都唔返屋企噉就啱。<br />\n<br />\n講吓戰績，十月頭磅過重為83KG, 十月中旬去咗歐遊2星期其本上日日行路，返到嚟接著開波減肥呢一星期，就係噉割咗2KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道嘅一刻真係開心到大叫咗一聲YES!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想試下keep著多約3-4個月，可否跌至75KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打有啲其他建議可以令小弟自己更fit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後再利申: 戒丁 Day 7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1426294698e2d0c1e7615bef9731810342985e97","tid":892088,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"屌，一齊減點睇"},{"pid":"9762094ed99b6e62fafb92324057a64bd1c8c5cc","tid":892088,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1426294698e2d0c1e7615bef9731810342985e97","tid":892088,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"屌，一齊減點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"Welcome<br />\n<br />\n欠女，只因欠身型"},{"pid":"a1eb8e55e05f3e101477868316af01afcda3555f","tid":892088,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪減肥法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}